变成水晶球)。小花因此住在人类世界，并化名为“新旗山花”，不过却因为调皮的个性，常常滥用魔法，被DoReMi等人多次警告。同时魔法堂受到先前小花改变自己的魔法影响，被改变成手工艺品店。趁势利用此机会，DoReMi等人要制纺织品，重现前前任女王送给她6个孙儿的礼物，从而唤起前前任女王在人间的美好回忆，进而消除六条荆棘，令沈睡中的前前任女王苏醒。 ","date":"2002-02-03","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/0e/e8/14878_1hWbu.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/0e/e8/14878_1hWbu.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/0e/e8/14878_1hWbu.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/0e/e8/14878_1hWbu.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/0e/e8/14878_1hWbu.jpg"},"rating":{"rank":174,"total":377,"score":8.2,"count":{"1":2,"2":1,"3":1,"4":2,"5":7,"6":31,"7":69,"8":83,"9":86,"10":95}},"tags":[{"name":"TV","count":128},{"name":"2002","count":113},{"name":"魔法少女","count":90},{"name":"原创","count":80},{"name":"五十岚卓哉","count":74},{"name":"东映","count":72},{"name":"童年","count":60},{"name":"東映アニメーション","count":54},{"name":"细田守","count":42},{"name":"TVB","count":41},{"name":"马越嘉彦","count":35}],"eps":51,"collection":{"wish":558,"collect":591,"doing":47,"on_hold":80,"dropped":59}},{"id":12982,"type":2,"name":"喜劇","name_cn":"喜剧","summary":"故事以爱尔兰独立战争为背景，小女孩的村子正面临凶残英军的铁蹄。\r\n凭借对传说中的恶魔城及黑剑士的天真的信仰，\r\n小女孩鼓起勇气带上一本喜剧，踏上寻找骑士的征程。\r\n有惊无险的交易成功后，黑剑士解决了前往村子的军队。\r\n若干年后小女孩回忆起了当年的事","date":"2002-02-05","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/7a/d2/12982_hT989.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/7a/d2/12982_hT989.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/7a/d2/12982_hT989.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/7a/d2/12982_hT989.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/7a/d2/12982_hT989.jpg"},"rating":{"rank":4578,"total":332,"score":6.6,"count":{"1":0,"2":1,"3":2,"4":5,"5":48,"6":95,"7":128,"8":40,"9":6,"10":7}},"tags":[{"name":"短片","count":153},{"name":"Studio4℃","count":107},{"name":"中泽一登","count":82},{"name":"2002","count":78},{"name":"OVA","count":74},{"name":"原创","count":39},{"name":"实验性短篇动画","count":30},{"name":"绿川光","count":30},{"name":"中澤一登","c